Class UMB

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
UBB, UBezierPatch, UColor, UColorHSP, UCurve, UDataGeo, UDataList, UDataPoint, UDataTag, UDataTagList, UDataTaxonomy, UEdge, UEdgeList, UFace, UFileStructure, UGeo, UGeoGenerator, UGeoGroup, UGeoIO, UGeomerative, UGeoTransformer, UHeading, UIntersections, UNav3D, UPoly2Tri, USubdivision, UTask, UTime, UTimeRange, UToxi, UVertex, UVertexList, UXML
public class UMB
extends java.lang.Object
implements UConst

UMB is the base class for most of the classes in ModelbuilderMk2, meaning that they all extend this class and thus inherit the capabilities it provides. This includes convenient tools for common computational tasks (math, string formatting etc), as well as a mechanism to set and share a PApplet instance provided by the user. Call setPApplet(PApplet) or setGraphics(PGraphics) to provide a PApplet or PGraphics instance,which can then be used by geometry classes like UGeo and UVertexList for rendering etc.

Author:
Marius Watz
